Two, burning in fire, Matatabi

00:00:18.980 --> 00:00:21.570
TWO TAILS MATATABI / YUGITO NI'I Two, burning in fire, Matatabi

00:00:21.730 --> 00:00:22.980
Three, leave the water to Isobu

00:00:22.980 --> 00:00:25.570
THREE TAILS ISOBU / YAGURA Three, leave the water to Isobu

